Package commands

Interface CommandInterface<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChangeDirectory, ClientUrl, Command, Concatenate, Copy, Echo, Exit, History, ListContents, LoadJShell, MakeDirectory, Manual, Move, PopDirectory, PrintWorkingDirectory, PushDirectory, Redirection, Remove, SaveJShell, Search, Tree
    public interface CommandInterface<T>
    CommandInterface is the interface which defines the structure of all commands, their constants and how to access them, and the method run to run them.
